snippet.textDisplay: The posture that some American governors--such as DeSantis of Florida--assume strikes me as reminiscent of the full title of Sranley Kubrick's 1964 film: "Dr. Strangelove, Or How I Learned To Stop Worrying And Love The Bomb," only today's version reads, "COVID, Or How I Learned To Stop Worrying And Love The Virus."
